Class QueryLists

  • java.lang.Object
    • query.QueryLists

  • public class QueryLists
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages all the Queries of the program.

    There are 3 main lists:

    • awaitingBuyQueries
    • awaitingSellQueries
    • successfullyFinishedQueries
